f"FEATURE REQUEST:\n{request_text}\n\nCODE CONTEXT:\n{context_str}\n\n"
                    "Break this request into an ordered list of implementation tasks.\n"
                    "Prefer the FEWEST tasks possible. A single API endpoint, service, or cohesive "
                    "change is ONE task — do NOT split it into per-file or per-layer subtasks "
                    "(controller/service/model/test all belong to the same task). Only create a "
                    "separate task when a part is genuinely independent, delivers distinct user-facing "
                    "value, or is a hard prerequisite the rest builds on. Most requests are 1-3 tasks; "
                    "returning a single task is the common, correct answer.\n\n"
                    "Return ONLY a JSON array, no prose, in this exact shape:\n"
                    '[{"slug": "short-kebab-slug", "title": "Human title", '
                    '"summary": "What this task builds and why", "deps": ["slug-of-prerequisite"]}]\n\n'
                    "Order tasks so that dependencies come before dependents. "
                    "Use slugs (not indices) in deps. Hard maximum 8 tasks, but fewer is better."

